title: Obama’s Weakness Paves Way for Russia to Leadership in Middle East
text: Having launched airstrikes against the Islamic State (ISIL) terrorist group in Syria, Russian President Vladimir Putin has, once again, totally outmaneuvered Barack Obama, journalist Charles Krauthammer wrote in his article for National Review. ...
